  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to determine the accuracy of two different continuous blood sugar&#xD;
      monitoring systems in hospitalized patients by comparing them standard laboratory blood sugar&#xD;
      testing in the hospital.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
